How do I remove NAs from my data?
‚û°Ô∏è For some functions, you can set the na.rm argument to remove NAs from the data. If you want to remove all observations with NAs, you can use the na.omit() function. Removing an observation means removing the entire data row.üëá(5/8) #rstats
